quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  11,72,"Naboola mbu: “Eh, esie endi! Ndakhebula nengofule endi, ne omusatsa wanje wuno nakofule ari? Toto lino nilikhuwa liokhuwuchisia.”"
  11,73,"Nibaboola mbu: “Owukanga likhuwa lia Nyasaye? Tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye nende tsikhabi tsitsie tsibe ninanyu enywe Abandu beyinzu ino. Toto Ye ni Wokhwitsomibwa muno, Woluyali po.”"
  11,74,"Mana shingala oburi bwawa khu Ibrahim, namalile okhunyoola akomwikhoyo ako, yachaka okhukhuyingasia efwe okhulondokhana nende abandu ba Luti."
  11,75,"Toto Ibrahim yali omwihotselefu muno, wokhwitsomia muno wa Nyasaye, omwangu wokhumukalushila."
  11,76,"(Nikhumuboolela mbu) “Ewe Ibrahim! Lekhana nende kano. Toto likhuwa lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi limalile okhwitsa. Ne toto abo shilaboolela eshinyasio eshilakalusibwa inyuma tawe.”"
  11,77,"Ne olwa Abarumwa befu betsela Luti, yabelela muno khulwa bo, mana nalola obutinyu muno shichila bo, naboola mbu: “Ino ni inyanga isiro muno.”"
  11,78,"Mana abandu bebe nibamwitsila tsimbilo, ne imbeli wa kano bali nibakholanga amabii. Naboola mbu: “Enywe Abandu banje, bano ni abakhana banje, bo ni abatswenufu muno khwinywe. Kho, rie Nyasaye, ne mulafimbia omurwe khubacheni banje tawe. Mwinywe shalikhomwo omusatsa omulunjifu tawe?”"
  11,79,"Nibaboola mbu: “Toto wamala okhumanya obulayi mbu khubula oluchendo lwosilwosi mubakhana bao, ne toto omanyile obulayi muno shiakhwenyanga.”"
  11,80,"Naboola mbu: “Embetsangakhwo naamaani khwinywe nohomba embetsanga neenyala okhwilushia khu isiilo ya amaani muno.”"
  11,81,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Luti, toto efwe khuli Abarumwa ba Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, shibalakhulakhwo tawe. Kho rula ewe nende Abandu bao, mumashebelende, ne Omundu yesiyesi mwinywe alahenga inyuma tawe, halali Omukhasi wuwo. Ye toto kalamunyoola amasila ketsa okhunyoola abandi abo. Toto ebise biabu ni mumabwibwi. Koo, amabwibwi shikalisa ahambii?”"